{"data":[{"date":"12:46 04/08","title":"U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 6-1 U16 Philippines (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm ... v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/video-tong-hop-u16-viet-nam-61-u16-philippines-u16-aff-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 4 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng A tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng sau U16 Myanmar \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A do ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-168-192170.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lich-thi-dau-u16-viet-nam-tai-giai-u16-dong-nam-a-2018-168-192170.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018: Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng BXH - LT\u0110 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM 6-1 U16 PHILIPPINES<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-Viet-Nam-6-1-U16-Philippines.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U16 \u0110\u00f4ng\u00a0Nam \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, ch\u00fang ta bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng may U16 Philippines y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eadm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi U16 Philippines bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eadp trung g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 7: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I \u0110\u1ea6U TI\u00caN. S\u1ed1 12 Thanh Trung treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a U16 Philippines v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 20 V\u0103n Th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-07.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 13: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang d\u1ed3n \u00e9p r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 20: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0. </strong>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, Quang\u00a0Tr\u01b0\u1eddng r\u00f3t b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0 V\u0103n\u00a0Th\u00f4ng lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 Philippines c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat b\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-20.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 24: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t pha uy hi\u1ebfp v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n U16 Philippines nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-24.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 28: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM N\u00c2NG T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0 L\u00caN 2-0. Trong m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0103n \u00fd, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0103ng ngang v\u00e0o trong cho s\u1ed1 11 Qu\u1ed1c Ho\u00e0ng, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o PVF v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng tung l\u01b0\u1edbi U16 Philippines.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-28.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 30: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1eaft volley k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-30.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 37: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I LI\u00caN TI\u1ebeP. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u00e2y h\u00e3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n U16 Philippines nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/154254-U16-viet-nam-phut-37.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 40: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM D\u1eaaN 3-0. </strong>Tuy v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c Ho\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-40.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HI\u1ec6P 2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 46: Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 4 cho U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U16 Philippines v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u thua ngay tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-46.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 51: U16 PHILIPPINES R\u00daT NG\u1eaeN C\u00c1CH BI\u1ec6T. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Duy D\u0169ng lao ra c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t qu\u1ea3 treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U16 Philippines d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-51.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 55: U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U16 Myanmar v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 58: U16 VI\u1ec6T NAM N\u00c2NG T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0 L\u00caN 4-1. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 4. S\u1ed1 8 \u0110\u1ee9c Ho\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 11 \u0110\u1ee9c Ho\u00e0ng c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa t\u00e2ng b\u00f3ng qua \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-58.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 67:\u00a0T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam v\u00e0i b\u00e0n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U16 Myanmar (g\u1eb7p U16 Campuchia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m tay).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 71: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I LI\u00caN TI\u1ebeP. U16 Philippines su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 volley ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \"t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m t\u1ef1 \u0103n\" d\u00e0nh cho s\u1ed1 16 Ng\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-71.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 80: T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0 \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C N\u00c2NG L\u00caN 5-1. </strong>Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc\u00a0Th\u00e0nh sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 7 V\u0103n Chung.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-80.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>- PH\u00daT 80+3: K\u1ebeT QU\u1ea2 \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C \u1ea4N \u0110\u1ecaNH 6-1.</strong> T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 5-1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c th\u00ec v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Qu\u1ed1c Ho\u00e0ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 6 cho\u00a0U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/4/U16-viet-nam-phut-83.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- D\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0ng U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, U16 Myanmar \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng U16 Campuchia 4-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng A nh\u1edd h\u01a1n ch\u00fang ta v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng - b\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u1eb7p ch\u00ednh U16 Myanmar, U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Philippines chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 48 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U16 Philippines chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 48 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/Truc-tiep-U16-Viet-Nam-vs-U16-Philippines-chieu-ngay-hom-nay-48-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Danh s\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec3n U16 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U16 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5073","checkdouble":"193698"},{"date":"15:14 04/08","title":"Bayern c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Octavio Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern Munich, Alphonso Davies. C\u1ef1u HLV Canada tin Bayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Davies</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Bayern Munich c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Alphonso Davies c\u1ee7a Vancouver Whitecaps. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 18 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y (sinh th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2000) s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Canada t\u1edbi h\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS n\u0103m 2018 r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Bayern v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2019.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 ngay cho Vancouver Whitecaps s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 11,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro. T\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d tr\u1ea3 cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Alphonso Davies c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i MLS.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Alphonso Davies h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Alphonso Davies h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/zambrano-phat-bieu-ve-tan-binh-bayern-alphonso-davies.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern, Davies</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y c\u0169 ng\u1ee3i khen sao tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlphonso Davies mang g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c Liberia, sinh t\u1ea1i Ghana song l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Canada ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Vancouver Whitecaps. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi c\u00f3 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Canada, anh \u0111\u00e3 ra m\u1eaft \u0110TQG n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 16, m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y c\u0169 t\u1ea1i \u0110T Canada, Octavio Zambrano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Bayern Munich, Alphonso Davies v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 60 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1eabn l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 h\u1eddi cho sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-khong-muon-mua-martial-172-193655.html\">Bayern t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i thanh l\u00fd sao v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap M.U</span><br>\r\n<span>Bayern kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua Martial. Ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Bild.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBayern \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec n\u1eefa. 100% \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt\u201d, Zambrano n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal. \u201cNh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng th\u0103ng hoa nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Alphonso Davies v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Davies ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea5p 3 t\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi nay, Davies c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n cho \u0110T Canada ch\u1ec9 sau 6 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o. Sao tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i teen t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i C\u00fap v\u00e0ng CONCACAF 2017 v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1edbi Bayern. HLV Zambrano kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a tr\u00f2 c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Davies l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n \u1edf 1/3 cu\u1ed1i s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi so v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bayern Munich tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bayern-munich-ngay-lap-tuc-ban-jerome-boateng-cho-mu-neu-172-192625.html\">Bayern Munich ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e1n Jerome Boateng cho MU n\u1ebfu....</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barcelona-dat-thoa-thuan-chieu-mo-arturo-vidal-180-192611.html\">\u0110\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Barca s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Arturo Vidal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-munich-mia-mai-juventus-phi-tien-vi-ong-gia-ronaldo-176-192582.html\">Bayern Munich m\u1ec9a mai Juventus ph\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u00ec \u201c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0\u201d Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5072","checkdouble":"193707"},{"date":"16:21 04/08","title":"V\u00ec sao c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat d\u1ea7n kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/vi-sao-cac-nha-dau-tu-trung-quoc-rut-khoi-bong-da-chau-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u00e2n Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt khi h\u00e0nh lang lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ef7 d\u00e2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung Qu\u1ed1c si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c m\u1ec1m, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Trung Qu\u1ed1c T\u1eadp C\u1eadn B\u00ecnh t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00f4ng qua con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Trung Qu\u1ed1c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00ec sao c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00ec sao c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Vi-sao-cac-nha-dau-tu-Trung-Quoc-rut-khoi-bong-da-chau-Au-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Trung Qu\u1ed1c, T\u1eadp C\u1eadn B\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c m\u1ec1m th\u00f4ng qua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea3o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng v\u1ee5 \u00e1p phe n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c doanh nh\u00e2n Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh lang lu\u1eadt ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 mua m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n, ho\u1eb7c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u1ed5 phi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Chinese Super League (gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Trung Qu\u1ed1c) t\u1eebng l\u00ean t\u1ee5c chi ra h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng &quot;\u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eeb n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t tr\u00e1i khi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eeda ti\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u01b0a t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. Th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1eb7t ra quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u &quot;h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf&quot; l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 thao, r\u1ea1p chi\u1ebfu phim v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee9 &quot;\u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh' n\u00e0y r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y&quot; - Mark Dreyer, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh trang &quot;China Sports Insider&quot; \u1edf B\u1eafc Kinh nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lan song dau tu ra bong da chau Au tung phat trien manh me o Trung Quoc.\" title=\"L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ra b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/tq-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>L\u00e0n s\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ra b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf Trung Qu\u1ed1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Th\u1eddi b\u00e1o T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1eeb 2014-17, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 chi ra kho\u1ea3ng 2.5 t\u1ec9 euro \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. H\u1ecd mua \u0111\u1ee9t Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan, Aston Villa, Northampton (gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng ba Anh) hay FC Sochaux-Montbeliard (Ligue 2) hay Slavia Prague (S\u00e9c).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u0169ng mua c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Manchester City v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid. Vi\u1ec7c Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn Tony Xia, nguy\u00ean Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aston Villa chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter sau khi b\u00e1n CLB: &quot;Hai th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Aston Villa&quot;.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 r\u00fat lui c\u1ee7a d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aston Villa l\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 th\u1ee9 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, ho\u1eb7c s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n \u0111ang n\u1eafm trong tay sau khi b\u1ecb si\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch. Nh\u1eefng CLB tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 AC Milan, Atletico Madrid, Slavia Prague v\u00e0 Northampton Town.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tony Xia dai dien cho viec cac nha dau tu Trung Quoc rut khoi bong da chau Au.\" title=\"Tony Xia \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/vi-sao-cac-nha-dau-tu-trung-quoc-rut-khoi-bong-da-chau-au.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Tony Xia \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrevor Watkins, m\u1ed9t lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a Pinsent Masons nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c doanh nh\u00e2n Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u phi\u00eau l\u01b0u. Nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi trung gian m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c thua l\u1ed7 \u1edf Aston Villa v\u00e0 AC Milan tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi r\u00fat lui. Aston Villa m\u1ea5t 130 tri\u1ec7u USD do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n 55% c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho t\u1ef7 ph\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp, Nassef Sawiris - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp ra qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Wes Edens.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00ean nh\u1edb h\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2016, Tony Xia ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ebfn 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac nha dau tu Trung Quoc tung chi rat nhieu tien de so huu cac doi bong o chau Au.\" title=\"C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eebng chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/ac.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li Yonghong c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u&nbsp;nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u do thi\u1ebfu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</span>.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLi Yonghong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi ra 740 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua AC Milan t\u1eeb Silvio Berlusconi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u00e0o tay Elliott Management - Qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Hoa K\u1ef3. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n do kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n vay l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t cao tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n 300 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">5USport, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1eebng n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Northampton c\u0169ng b\u00e1n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 sau 9 th\u00e1ng. \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho vi\u1ec7c &quot;h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i&quot; d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngu\u1ed3n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u1ef7 ph\u00fa Wang Jianlin l\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n khi b\u00e1n 17% c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng Hai nh\u1eb1m thu h\u1ed3i v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Fosun, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu Wolverhampton khi mua l\u1ea1i CLB v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u USD n\u0103m 2016 c\u0169ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League 2018-19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cac nha dau tu Trung Quoc duoc khuyen dau tu cho bong da quoc noi de hop long chinh phu hon.\" title=\"C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p l\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 h\u01a1n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/tq-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p l\u00f2ng ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 h\u01a1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u00edt \u1ecfi kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf d\u00f2ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. Nikki Wang, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u1ec3 thao Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Deloitte nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nikki Wang nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 do &quot;m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1p l\u00fd thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;. B\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n ra n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u00ean l\u00e0m vui l\u00f2ng Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho ch\u00ednh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cau-thu-tre-goc-viet-chon-khoac-ao-tuyen-u19-trung-quoc-168-192245.html\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n U19 Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\">Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/arsenal-bi-lua-ngoan-muc-khi-ky-hop-dong-voi-cong-ty-trung-quoc-188-191555.html\">Arsenal b\u1ecb l\u1eeba ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cong-ty-trung-quoc-mat-12-trieu-usd-vi-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-465-191378.html\">C\u00f4ng ty Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t 12 tri\u1ec7u USD v\u00ec Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/futsal-viet-nam-huy-diet-trung-quoc-o-giai-tu-hung-168-189363.html\">Futsal Vi\u1ec7t Nam &lsquo;h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t&rsquo; Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5071","checkdouble":"193652"},{"date":"14:14 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Juventus 05h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-juventus-05h00-ngay-58-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid vs Juventus l\u00fac 05h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Juventus 05h00 ng\u00e0y 58 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Juventus 05h00 ng\u00e0y 58 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/141236-Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real Madrid vs Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Real Madrid vs Juventus: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Real Madrid ra qu\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c HLV Julen Lopetegui mang sang M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Tuy v\u1eady, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Manchester United \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00f3a \u0111i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u, khi Los Blancos ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y ngay c\u00f9ng HLV m\u1edbi. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn t\u1eeb g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh v\u1edbi \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 Lopetegui mang \u0111\u1ebfn. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u0103ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos, Marco Asensio c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. D\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111em t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem trong c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd d\u00e0n tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00e2u cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMadridista c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u00edch m\u1eaft m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 Lopetegui v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u2013 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong h\u00e0nh l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo khi chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, khi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u2013 Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuve c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u00e0 Ronaldo ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 d\u00f9 trong tay HLV Massimiliano Allegri v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ICC 2018 \u2013 c\u00f9ng Olympique Lyon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bayern Munich (th\u1eafng 2-0) v\u00e0 Benfica (th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m), Allegri \u0111\u1ec1u thay t\u1eeb 9 \u0111\u1ebfn 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 khi bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, ngo\u00e0i Ronaldo, Paulo Dybala, Juan Cuadrado, Rodrigo Bentancur, Douglas Costa, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca, Blaise Matuidi c\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u1eadp \u1edf Turin ho\u1eb7c v\u1eabn trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf M\u1ef9, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Juve kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Gianluigi Buffon khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t \u0111i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Giorgio Chiellini, Andre Bazargli hay Medhi Benatia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Real Madrid, Allegri s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh khi \u00f4ng \u0111ang th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3 \u2013 nh\u1eb1m th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi Ronaldo sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fac Lopetegui tung to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t. V\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xen k\u1ebd m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 tr\u1ebb, t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin cho h\u1ecd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Juve \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo, c\u00f3 Lopetegui v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Buffon, n\u00ean s\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1eabn \u0111ong \u0111\u1ea7y. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u1ebfu thi\u1ebfu b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n* L\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Real Madrid: Kh\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng,  Sergio Ramos ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng; Marcelo, Casemiro, Raphael Varane, Luka  Modric, Mateo Kovacic ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n- Juventus: Kh\u00f4ng  tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng; Paulo Dybala, Juan Cuadrado, Rodrigo  Bentancur, Douglas Costa, Mario Mandzukic, Marko Pjaca, Blaise Matuidi,  Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng tham gia tour du \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u<br>\r\n<br>\r\n-  Juventus c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ICC 2018 n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng Real Madrid v\u00e0 Lyon kh\u00f4ng  th\u1eafng 1 trong 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Real Madrid ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n- 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (\u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Champions League), Real Madrid th\u1eafng 3, Juve th\u1eafng 2.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5070","checkdouble":"193706"},{"date":"14:22 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Barca 07h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-ac-milan-vs-barca-07h05-ngay-58-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Milan vs Barca l\u00fac 07h05 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Barca 07h05 ng\u00e0y 58 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh AC Milan vs Barca 07h05 ng\u00e0y 58 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/ac-milan-vs-barcelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">AC Milan vs Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>AC Milan vs Barca: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>3 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Barca, Milan m\u1ea5t trung v\u1ec7 Bonucci cho Juventus. Theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Rossoneri \u0111\u00f3n 2 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb L\u00e3o b\u00e0 l\u00e0 Caldara \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng Higuain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda Barcelona, tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Aleix Vidal \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea5t Bonucci l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Milan \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Barcelona. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, m\u1ea5t Aleix Vidal kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Barca b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh TBN n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ebfn Nou Camp v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi World Cup 2018 n\u00ean Milan k\u00e9o qu\u00e2n sang M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec World Cup, HLV Valverde \u0111em sang M\u1ef9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 h\u00f9ng h\u1eadu nh\u01b0ng Milan ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf ICC 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn 2 tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U v\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ebfn M\u1ef9 v\u1edbi qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 thi\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Messi, Pique, Alba v\u00e0 Busquets\u2026, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ecdc c\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1eabn g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Barca \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadt v\u1eadt Tottenham sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u00e0 thua AS Roma xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a HLV Valverde. Ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 Tottenham v\u00e0 Roma (lu\u00f4n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7) nh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Valverde (tung h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0o thay) khi\u1ebfn Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0o tay 2 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng phanh c\u1ee7a Milan trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng danh gi\u00e1 Champions League, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda v\u1edbi k\u00ec ph\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 Barcelona. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00ed do v\u00ec sao cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Milan \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Barca trong 5 n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013, Barca \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Milan 3-1 thu\u1ed9c Champions League. Trong l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u1edf ICC 2018 n\u00e0y, Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1eeda tr\u00ean so v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00ed n\u1ebfu Barca ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham v\u00e0 AS Roma. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu HLV Valverde tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Arthur, Rafinha, Munir, Sergi Roberto v\u00e0 Semedo v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong c\u1ea3 90 ph\u00fat\u2026 th\u00ec m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Milan.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5069","checkdouble":"193708"},{"date":"14:07 04/08","title":"Barca c\u00f3 Vidal, Valverde vui nh\u01b0 \u201cm\u1edf c\u1edd trong b\u1ee5ng\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal, t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barcelona. HLV 54 tu\u1ed5i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vidal gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarcelona m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Arturo Vidal t\u1eeb Bayern Munich. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ph\u1ea3i chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u00ean trang web ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Barca th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Vidal theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c, Vidal s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Barca. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 31, c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Leverkusen v\u00e0 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Bayern v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ernesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nValverde vui m\u1eebng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 Vidal \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 anh r\u1ea5t \u00f4ng. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng 31 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho Blaugrana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u201d, Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m khi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i qua.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVidal \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin Vidal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p cho Paulinho, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Barca. \u201cC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Paulinho, Vidal l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi nhanh ch\u00f3ng\u201d, Valverde n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 cho nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat tranh c\u00e3i khi Paulinho \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra s\u00e2n. Sau \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\">Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/thu-mon-barcelona-tham-vong-qua-mat-ca-messi-180-192583.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Barcelona tham v\u1ecdng qua m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ter-stegen-phat-bieu-ve-real-180-192570.html\">Sao Barca b\u1ed7ng d\u01b0ng \u201cn\u1ed1i gi\u00e1o cho gi\u1eb7c\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-la-ben-do-hoan-hao-cua-mignolet-180-192544.html\">Barca l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Mignolet</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nhan-don-dau-vu-rabiot-180-192514.html\">Barca nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5068","checkdouble":"193703"},{"date":"17:47 04/08","title":"Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/4/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u euro. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Arturo Vidal c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern Munich sau khi ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVidal tri \u00e2n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arturo Vidal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthu, Malcom v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 Lenglet. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Bayern Munich sau 3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 18 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong 124 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern v\u00e0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c C\u0110V&rdquo; &ndash; Vidal chia s\u1ebb. &ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Munich. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi, cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vidal c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern Munich sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca\" title=\"Vidal c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern Munich\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vidal c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern Munich sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, G\u0110\u0110H c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, \u00f4ng Karl-Heinz Rummenigge c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Arturo v\u00ec 3 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Bayern. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhau, v\u00e0 Arturo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Anh \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 CLB lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Arturo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Franck Ribery c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tri \u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Vidal c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Bayern Munich: &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em, c\u1eadu kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u1edb c\u1eadu \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u1eadu l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t cao qu\u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1eadu l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh, m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda CLB Barcelona, h\u1ecd d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthu, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Arturo Vidal s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, d\u00f9 anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd tiki-taka. Vidal l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p cho Paulinho, c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Trung Qu\u1ed1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Barca \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay m\u1ed9t Vidal kh\u00e1c. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Aleix Vidal \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal-180-193703.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-phat-bieu-ve-vidal-180-193703.html\">Barca c\u00f3 Vidal, Valverde vui nh\u01b0 &ldquo;m\u1edf c\u1edd trong b\u1ee5ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nErnesto Valverde ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arturo Vidal, t\u00e2n binh m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Barcelona. HLV 54 tu\u1ed5i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span><br>\r\nBarca mua Arturo Vidal th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5067","checkdouble":"193716"},{"date":"14:08 04/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Lazio 01h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nhan-dinh-arsenal-vs-lazio-01h00-ngay-58-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal vs Lazio l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 5/8 (Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Lazio 01h00 ng\u00e0y 58 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal vs Lazio 01h00 ng\u00e0y 58 Giao h\u1eefu CLB h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/180804_092943_254.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arsenal vs Lazio</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Arsenal vs Lazio: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi Unai Emery ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Emirates v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 so s\u00e1nh Arsenal m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Arsenal c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Arsene Wenger. S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec1 cao t\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery. H\u1ecd t\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi th\u1eddi Wenger. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng Arsenal theo h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Emery l\u00e0 Lucas Torreira. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1,68m) nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u00ec nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Torreira th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Uruguay \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcello Donatelli, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Torreira \u1edf Pescara th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u1ec9 sau Sergio Busquets. N\u00f3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i thay cho Arsenal sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Wenger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 Lucas Torreira, Arsenal c\u1ea7n 1 s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Lazio \u0111\u00eam nay \u1edf Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Unai Emery l\u1eafp gh\u00e9p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay v\u00e0o s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng may cho Emery l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Granit Xhaka. Xhaka v\u00e0 Torreira c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9nh cho s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. Torreira ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Xhaka l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o l\u00f9i s\u00e2u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 HLV Emery ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, n\u00f3 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn cho Arsenal, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Emery \u0111ang kh\u01a1i d\u1eady nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Ozil, Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Aubameyang \u1edf h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLazio l\u00e0 b\u00e0i test ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Arsenal th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Roma kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Simone Inzaghi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua, Lazio \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Arsenal c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o trong 90 ph\u00fat d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Unai Emery. M\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng xem v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 li\u1ec1u thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19 v\u1edbi Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPHONG \u0110\u1ed8 V\u00c0 \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Arsenal kh\u00f4ng thua trong 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n- Lazio to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n- \u1ede l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2007, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Lazio v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5066","checkdouble":"193704"},{"date":"14:42 04/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp CLB h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/lucas-nmecha-sap-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Sao tr\u1ebb U19 Anh r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd theo ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Harrison t\u1edbi Leeds United c\u1ee7a HLV Marcelo Bielsa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Guardiola th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bielsa</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Marcelo Bielsa. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Argentina c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Guardiola hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb Bielsa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do sau khi Bielsa t\u1edbi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Leeds United, Guardiola d\u00e0nh cho \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u01b0u \u00e1i. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City \u0111\u1ec3 Jack Harrison t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Elland Road d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ch\u00ednh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Lucas-Nmecha-sap-roi-Man-City-duoi-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Guardiola th\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bielsa c\u1ee7a Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGuardiola tin r\u1eb1ng phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Leeds s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Man City. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd b\u00e1u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nmecha s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Leeds</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGuardiola s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho Leeds m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Man City n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Lucas Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Bielsa d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Man City v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Nmecha cua Man City\" title=\"Lucas Nmecha cua Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/lucas-nmecha-sap-roi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nmecha s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNmecha sinh cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 1998, t\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Anh sinh t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c song gia nh\u1eadp l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Man City khi m\u1edbi 9 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Anh, Nmecha c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Leeds, nh\u1eefng Swansea, Blackburn v\u00e0 West Brom t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Nmecha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft gi\u1eefa hai HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng West Yorkshire v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/guardiola-phat-bieu-ve-harrison-172-192399.html\">Guardiola m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho sao tr\u1ebb Man City ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chot-gia-ban-day-bat-ngo-cho-joe-hart-172-192394.html\">Man City ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Joe Hart</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-chieu-mo-sao-juventus-172-192204.html\">Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hanh-dong-nay-cua-john-stones-khien-pep-mung-roi-nuoc-mat-172-192039.html\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a John Stones khi\u1ebfn Pep m\u1eebng r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city-172-191995.html\">V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5065","checkdouble":"193705"},{"date":"17:05 04/08","title":"Sao Chelsea ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/morata-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Morata ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlvaro Morata gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2017 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Chelsea. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London song ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a 2017/18, Morata c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 48 tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n b\u1ecb mai m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a anh. Morata b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alvaro Morata ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/morata-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, Morata m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0o tay Olivier Giroud. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge ngay trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 thay b\u1eb1ng Maurizio Sarri. Morata t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00e1c. \u201cNgay ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Chelsea, Marina Granovskaia. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u00f5 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB\u201d, t\u1edd Mirror tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Morata.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata co them co hoi khang dinh minh o Chelsea\" title=\"Morata c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/morata-quyet-dinh-soc-ngay-truoc-them-mua-giai-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Anh quy\u1ebft kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e0 \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u1eadu v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf London song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t c\u0103n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u1edf g\u1ea7n trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Cobham.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ee3 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Khi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd th\u00eam t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt (tr\u1eadn Community Shield v\u1edbi Man City)\u201d.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018-172-193673.html\">HLV Sarri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-se-roi-chelsea-cap-ben-real-o-he-2018-172-193672.html\">Courtois s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ac-milan-hoi-mua-mateo-kovacic-176-193644.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh sao Real v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chinh-thuc-gia-han-voi-tru-cot-172-193637.html\">Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-courtois-172-192624.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5064","checkdouble":"193712"},{"date":"17:21 04/08","title":"Sarri mu\u1ed1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/sarri-muon-khoi-dau-trieu-dai-bang-danh-hieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man xanh, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea \u2013 HLV Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u cho tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Pep Guardiola<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00f4n th\u1edd l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, tr\u1eadn tranh si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o HLV Maurizio Sarri &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t. Tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 HLV n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Anh. Premier League l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y? T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean\" title=\"HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/sarri-muon-khoi-dau-trieu-dai-bang-danh-hieu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Pep \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u0103m Arrigo Sacchi, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Pep l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ho\u1eb7c \u00edt ra c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1ecfi nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n: Man City \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft trong 2 n\u0103m qua, c\u00f2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 2 tu\u1ea7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t su\u00f4n s\u1ebb n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u00f4i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o CLB. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y 10 n\u0103m ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 do \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea-172-193663.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-thua-nhan-la-fan-cung-cua-thuyen-truong-chelsea-172-193663.html\">Pep th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 fan c\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00f4n th\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Pep ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 Sarri v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho HLV Chelsea nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-hoi-danh-cho-sarri-truoc-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-voi-man-city-172-193661.html\">3 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi d\u00e0nh cho Sarri tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap v\u1edbi Man City</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Man City trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a The Blues d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ng\u1ed5n ngang nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1....</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5063","checkdouble":"193714"},{"date":"17:32 04/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Everton kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m ch\u1ea5p Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/tan-binh-cua-everton-khang-dinh-khong-them-chap-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Lucas Digne m\u1ec9a mai Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nDigne m\u00f3c m\u1ec9a Liverpool<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Everton t\u1eeb Barca, v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf ch\u1ed7 trong bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, Digne \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m tr\u00ean ng\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &ldquo;I never walk alone (T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c). \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i g\u1ea7n gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi slogan c\u1ee7a Liverpool l\u00e0 &ldquo;You&rsquo;ll never walk alone&rdquo;. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Digne th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m g\u00ec v\u1edbi The Kop, v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Digne m\u1ec9a mai Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh\" title=\"Digne k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Everton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/tan-binh-cua-everton-khang-dinh-khong-them-chap-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Digne m\u1ec9a mai Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i ra m\u1eaft n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Merseyside, c\u1ef1u sao Barca r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V nh\u00e0 vui m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c m\u1ec9a mai Liverpool. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;H\u00ecnh x\u0103m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi h\u1ecd. N\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool ph\u1eadt l\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u1ecd 2 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 3 hay 4 tu\u1ed5i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 cha m\u1eb9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m, m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi Lucas Digne m\u1ec9a mai Liverpool trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Everton, anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ban \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Marco Silva \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Everton m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Wolves v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-hanh-dong-cuc-dep-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-193633.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/day-hanh-dong-cuc-dep-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-hanh-dong-cuc-dep-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-193633.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Alisson \u1edf Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Loris Karius.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-sao-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-172-192488.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/chinh-thuc-sao-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-sao-barca-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-172-192488.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Sao Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro</span><br>\r\nEverton mua Lucas Digne th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5062","checkdouble":"193715"},{"date":"09:33 04/08","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/cong-phuong-noi-gi-sau-man-len-dong-truoc-palestine.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p to l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/38230725_10209976210556579_816878594738356224_n_ntub-2218.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 tung ch\u00e2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Palestine ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cH\u00f4m nay c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a em r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 vui v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho em gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-palestine-noi-gi-khi-thua-nguoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193688.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Palestine n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110T U23 Palestine cho r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/thang-palestin-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/thang-palestine-hlv-park-hang-seo-van-so-lo-bai-292-193667.html\">Th\u1eafng Palestine, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn s\u1ee3 l\u1ed9 b\u00e0i</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng U23 Palestine v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toa-sang-truoc-palestine-cong-phuong-duoc-ca-ngoi-het-loi-168-193668.html\">T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span><br>\r\nThi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ca ng\u1ee3i v\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5061","checkdouble":"193691"}]}